{"tid":2314932,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（上年講過）鎖港唔比人同錢走係將來會發生","createTime":"2020-12-07T01:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T06:51:08.000Z","uid":76310,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c6cf4a541e06ffcf3e2511a0de631908822c5728","tid":2314932,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:13:10.000Z","msg":"上年陳同佳事件 上年講過抄家會5年內發生<br />\n結果只用一年便實踐左預言<br />\n之前預言過5年內會出現大鎖港，好似強国咁限制金錢和人員流動，唔係唔比走，但要經過上級批准<br />\n我既推論係錢和人流走太多，港共頂唔住，要鎖住人同錢唔比走<br />\n設30萬人走，每人假設走資50萬（現金，強迫金，賣樓既錢，賣股票既錢等）<br />\n=300000*500000=150，000，000，000<br />\n大家自己睇路<br />\n武肺一過，大隊就會走<br />\n777覺得香港人唔會走，覺得香港好好，d人唔會捨得走，睇下是否如此"},{"pid":"dad8c5b10b73406ea0691ae9a6f250bcb3bb6f35","tid":2314932,"uid":276839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"咁連到時都唔反枱就真係抵撚死啦。"},{"pid":"ae5f62f9a63399ed9e38496183d902ccf42dd099","tid":2314932,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:19:40.000Z","msg":"777真心覺得香港好好<br />\n覺得佢治下香港好完美<br />\nD人唔捨得走"},{"pid":"e27399ebe5d5dec3f60d79b738320cb190af2db5","tid":2314932,"uid":38172,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得打哂出頭鳥就收工, 之後就全力谷經濟, 有留意市況, 人仔而家升返哂, 匯豐又升返, 恆指上返27000,港紙M3創新高, 美元指數就日日跌<br />\n<br />\n仲叫我信連登仔?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74e101eb906fec6f7a7fe1f829565ce57002bc1","tid":2314932,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"防疫為由禁出境<br />\n好似599G咁玩"},{"pid":"d96a4fc1b575722068a3283d8ad12a3f7ad1a77c","tid":2314932,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"每人走得50萬咁少?&nbsp;你係咪講緊50萬美金/英鎊呀?<br />\n<br />\n睇個勢點止走30萬人咁少,&nbsp;我話50萬人起計, 支共係咁玩加速, 話唔埋5年後走過百萬人<br />\n<br />\n下年外國全民免費武漢肺炎疫苗後開返關,&nbsp;D港豬仲唔一窩峰咁湧去英國加拿大澳洲,&nbsp;一年都可以走你30萬人,&nbsp;今次輪到香港人玩大逃港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83087023fb98c870f1e03c7ea69f0afa4b558ff","tid":2314932,"uid":293227,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"MPF 遲早被共產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aea22b45d43f585dba6d4300b499e15e8418986","tid":2314932,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d96a4fc1b575722068a3283d8ad12a3f7ad1a77c","tid":2314932,"uid":198175,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"每人走得50萬咁少?&nbsp;你係咪講緊50萬美金/英鎊呀?<br />\n<br />\n睇個勢點止走30萬人咁少,&nbsp;我話50萬人起計, 支共係咁玩加速, 話唔埋5年後走過百萬人<br />\n<br />\n下年外國全民免費武漢肺炎疫苗後開返關,&nbsp;D港豬仲唔一窩峰咁湧去英國加拿大澳洲,&nbsp;一年都可以走你30萬人,&nbsp;今次輪到香港人玩大逃港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"學生，年青人無乜錢<br />\n平均數差唔多啦"},{"pid":"ef8d0a99bfd3b91004b0f8fa18dcbcf53c5c7566","tid":2314932,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"睇下大家會唔會走<br />\n定真係好似777咁講 香港好好 唔捨得走"},{"pid":"44ce096b89d0ba42f8b5b5d09c7fab1a0ab90a4b","tid":2314932,"uid":326779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T01:57:29.000Z","msg":"人走ok! 錢留低！"},{"pid":"e3112654f52e8e019ff7ac6b31018ee90b0171f4","tid":2314932,"uid":47614,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">樓主推斷咁嚴謹 <br />\n考車應該難唔到你</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e48aeb06274d6aafeedf293ec64332aa481f237","tid":2314932,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike"